# Squad Infra

## Dominio

Alicerce tecnico do backend: scaffold NestJS, Docker, schema Prisma completo, Redis, Elasticsearch, guards globais, interceptors, health checks.

**Fonte de verdade:** PLANO.md secoes 1.1-1.10 (schema completo), 2.1 (infraestrutura), Stack, Portas Locais
**Fase PLANO:** F1 (construcao) + ownership continuo

---

## Entidades/Recursos sob responsabilidade

| Recurso | Secao PLANO | Descricao |
|---|---|---|
| docker-compose.yml | Stack, Portas Locais | PostgreSQL 16 + Redis 7 + Elasticsearch 8 |
| Schema Prisma completo | 1.1-1.10 | Todos os enums + models + indices + relacoes |
| DatabaseModule / PrismaService | 2.1 | Soft-delete middleware, @Global |
| ConfigModule | 2.1 | Validacao de env vars (DATABASE_URL, JWT secrets, REDIS, ES, PF) |
| CommonModule | 2.1 | Guards, Interceptors, Filters, Pipes, Decorators, PaginationDto |
| main.ts | 2.1 | Helmet, CORS, ValidationPipe, Swagger, prefixo /api/v1 |
| BullMQ + Redis | 2.1 | Filas: sync, reports, search-reindex |
| Elasticsearch setup | 2.1, 2.13 | Container + ElasticsearchModule + health check |
| Throttler | 2.1 | Rate limiting global |
| RequestId | 2.1 | UUID por request, header X-Request-Id |
| Health checks | F1 stories | GET /health, GET /health/ready |

