## Ordem de Execucao

### Etapa 1 — Scaffold + Docker (Daniel, solo)

- `nest new mundial-erp-api` (porta 3001)
- docker-compose.yml com PostgreSQL 16, Redis 7, Elasticsearch 8 (conforme PLANO Stack)
- .env com todas as variaveis (conforme PLANO 2.1)
- Validar: `docker-compose up` sobe os 3 servicos

### Etapa 2 — Paralelo (Fernanda + Pedro + Juliana)

```
Fernanda: Schema Prisma completo (secoes 1.1-1.10 do PLANO) + prisma migrate dev
Pedro:    CommonModule completo (guards, interceptors, filters, pipes, decorators)
Juliana:  ConfigModule + BullMQ setup + ElasticsearchModule
```

### Etapa 3 — Integracao (Daniel + Marcos)

- Daniel: main.ts (Helmet, CORS, ValidationPipe, Swagger, prefixo /api/v1), app.module.ts imports
- Marcos: Health checks (GET /health, GET /health/ready), Throttler, RequestId interceptor, testes

